data.description: Motivated Seller! Welcome Home to this charming MOVE-IN ready located in the quiet Oak Grove Estates neighborhood! This beautiful home boasts three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms with tons of outdoor space to entertain family and friends located in the award winning Bullard ISD. This home, built as a Parade Home, has 2241 square feet of living space and sits on a very large lot at .9 acres for ultimate privacy or building your dream backyard oasis. The beautiful open concept home has many upgrades such as 10' and 12' ceilings, 6" double stacked crown molding throughout, granite countertops in the kitchen, bathrooms and laundry room, as well as handscraped hardwood floors and fabulous stack stone wood burning fireplace. The large eat-in kitchen features a large granite top bar and breakfast room for casual dining, as well as a formal dining area for larger gatherings. Other features include built-in bookshelves, ceiling mounted surround sound, central vacuum, gladiator garage system for maximum garage storage and organization and custom window treatments, including two sets of beautiful wooden plantation shutters. A grand foyer with 12' ceiling and coat closet welcomes your guests and there is a side porch entry into the kitchen that gives the house a very homey feel. The split bedroom design offers a very large master bedroom has a fabulous dome ceiling with hidden lighting and features a double door entry into the ensuite master bathroom. You will enjoy the separate double walk-in closets, a walk-in shower with bench seating, double vanity and jetted tub. Tiled porches add a welcoming touch at every entry, including the back patio. The large wall of windows in the living area overlook the covered back patio and large backyard with mature trees and tons of wildlife. The extra long driveway, sidewalks and brick flowerbeds give this home lots of nice curb appeal.
